###

### TEST 3: Produkty z trackingStrategy=IndividuallyTracked
### Konwersja: IndividuallyTracked → INDIVIDUALLY_TRACKED
### Oczekiwane: Produkty z IndividuallyTracked
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?trackingStrategy=IndividuallyTracked HTTP/1.1

###

### TEST 4: Produkty z trackingStrategy=BatchTracked
### Konwersja: BatchTracked → BATCH_TRACKED
### Oczekiwane: Produkty z BatchTracked (Hejnalica + usługi + pakiety)
